  "title": "ISic004349. I.Sicily inscription 004349",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Simona Stoyanova</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">...</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.1)</span>ἔζησε [ἔτη <span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.5)</span>ΚΕ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Simona Stoyanova</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">···</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;ΕΖΗΣΕ[...<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ΚΕ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic004349_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, 2016-05-12, courtesy Museo di Archeologia dell'Universita di Catania\" src=\"ISic004349_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic004349.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, 2016-05-12, courtesy Museo di Archeologia dell'Universita di Catania\" src=\"ISic004349-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic004349_rear_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, 2016-05-12, courtesy Museo di Archeologia dell'Universita di Catania\" src=\"ISic004349_rear_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic004349_rear.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, 2016-05-12, courtesy Museo di Archeologia dell'Universita di Catania\" src=\"ISic004349_rear-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text from autopsy</span></span>; </li><li><span class=\"1\">1: <span>Biondi: ........; on the stone, traces of a stroke descending lower right (Χ, Σ, Κ, Ε all seem possible) and then two vertical strokes the first close to the preceding stroke, the second well separated.</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Biondi and Buscemi Felici 2014 170-171 no. 238 fig. 41 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002149\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002149</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Traces of letters on the first line suggest a lunate sigma, as the other attested sigma and both epsilons are also lunate.</p> Line 1  26-30  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
